title: QFold: Protein Folding with Quantm Walks
subtitle: QFold, A protein-folding method based on quantum walks
description: Implementation of QFold: protein folding using Szegedy-type quantum walks combined with deep learning. The quantum walk explores structure space more efficiently than classical search; the notebook implements and runs the algorithm.
friendly_name: QFold: Protein Folding with Quantm Walks
